snippet.title: Let's Play- Aurore: Five Princes Pt. 1- I'm a freaking witch queen!
snippet.description:
Hey Guys, It's Elric Atchison! I voiced Dr. Marcus Marshall in Aurore: Five Princes.  I had a lot of fun voicing Dr. Marcus Marshall in this visual novel. It is available on itch.io for free if you are wanting to play a dating sim. The visual novel is available since Yesterday Morning.  The game here was released on the day that I have my head-shot from C Sharp Productions in my home town.  

Discord: https://discord.gg/5RZ6u3F8
YT Channel: https://www.youtube.com/c/Elreezy
Twitch: https://twitch.tv/VAElricAtchison

My wife in the visual novel is voiced by Katie Otten. 

Game Info from itch.io:
"We were in our own little world, the world of the fae, and all of the danger that entailed."

Five Princes is a Renpy dating sim visual novel about witches, werewolves, vampires and other fantasy races.

You play as Daphne (customizable name) Marshall, a normal teenage girl. On the eve on your eighteenth birthday, you discover that not only are you a witch, you are the new empress of the fae.

But danger lies in wait,  and you have only a few short weeks to master your power and defend your empire.

Features:
• Six romance options (five male, one female)
• Choice to turn adult content on and off
• Partial voice acting
• Unlockable polyamorous relationship
• ~12 endings
• 60 CGs 
• Hidden romance option
•  ~126, 000 words

Link: 
https://peanutparade.itch.io/aurore-five-princes


If you want to contact me for voice over work

Elric T. Atchison
408-966-3211
Email: magicmastere@gmail.com
